enums.name: AutoGeneratedDomainNameLabelScope

values.name: NoReuse
values.doc: The domain name label is randomly generated. The resource name cannot be reused within the same region.

values.name: TenantReuse
values.doc: The domain name label is deterministically generated using the resource name and tenant id. The resource name cannot be reused within the same region and tenant.

values.name: SubscriptionReuse
values.doc: The domain name label is deterministically generated using the resource name, tenant id, and subscription id. The resource name cannot be reused within the same region and subscription.

values.name: ResourceGroupReuse
values.doc: The domain name label is deterministically generated using the resource name, tenant id, subscription id, and resource group name. The resource name cannot be reused within the same resource group.

enums.doc: The scope at which the auto-generated domain name label is generated and at which the resource name can be reused.
